description: Bones Burgers specializes in serving cincy residents the tastiest grass fed beef burgers in town. In addition, they also offer turkey, salmon, and garden burgers as well as a delectable grilled cheese sandwich. All burgers are served on locally baked whole grained bread, with a choice of 10-15 different cheeses and other locally sourced toppings. Compliment your delicious burger with seasoned parmesan fries or sweet potato fries.
name: Bones Burgers
